summary: Shana is a rogue that works well with stealth and Sadira is an OP tank that works with a magic class.
descriptionHtml:
Shana is a rogue that works well with stealth and Sadira is an OP tank that works with a magic class both can be found in riverwood this is my first mod of skyrim and i hope you all enjoy it. Also both of the followers can be marred too.

I deleted the old version for this new one. This is the first update. The new dungeon is a work in progress. I well also be working on Sadira Quest.

Update 1

Shana Quest- Family Jewels

New Dungeon- Stubby\'s Hideout
